Eilis Dillon Author Biography - Information About the Author

Eil√≠s Dillon, born 1920 and 1994, is listed in Hubin's crime and mystery fiction guide but we've taken this bibliography well beyond Hubin and the scope of crime fiction so this should be a complet e list of books in order of publication.
